  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"it\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\">\n  <meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"light dark\">\n  <title>Frontaliere Weekly</title>\n  <!--[if mso]><style>table{border-collapse:collapse;}td{padding:0;}</style><![endif]-->\n  <style>\n    body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#f1f5f9;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;}\n    table{border-collapse:collapse;}\n    img{border:0;max-width:100%;}\n    .preheader{display:none!important;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;max-height:0;max-width:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;}\n    @media only screen and (max-width:620px){\n      .outer-table{width:100%!important;}\n      .hero-rate{font-size:40px!important;}\n      .rate-box{padding:16px 20px!important;}\n      .section-pad{padding-left:16px!important;padding-right:16px!important;}\n      .topbar-pad{padding-left:16px!important;padding-right:16px!important;}\n      .metric-card{display:block!important;width:100%!important;padding:0 0 8px 0!important;}\n      .metric-row td{display:block!important;width:100%!important;padding:0 0 8px 0!important;}\n      .tool-cell{display:block!important;width:100%!important;padding:0 0 10px 0!important;}\n      .tool-row td{display:block!important;width:100%!important;padding:0 0 10px 0!important;}\n      .job-title{white-space:normal!important;}\n      .footer-pad{padding:20px 16px!important;}\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"preheader\">CHF/EUR 0.9420 · giovedì 14 maggio 2026&nbsp;‌‌‌‌‌‌‌</div>\n  <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f1f5f9;\">\n    <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;\">\n      <table width=\"620\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:620px;background:#ffffff;\">\n        \n    <tr><td class=\"topbar-pad\" style=\"background:#0f172a;padding:10px 28px;\">\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n        <td style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:900;color:#f97316;letter-spacing:-0.3px;\">Frontaliere Ticino</td>\n        <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#64748b;\">#71 · 14 mag. 2026</td>\n      </tr></table>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#0f172a;color:#fff;padding:32px 28px 28px;text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;color:#f97316;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;\">⚡ Aggiornamento in tempo reale</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.2;color:#fff;\">Buongiorno, frontaliere.</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;margin:0 0 20px;\">Ecco cosa succede ai tuoi soldi questa settimana.</div>\n\n      <!--[if mso]><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\"><tr><td style=\"background:#1e293b;border-radius:16px;padding:20px 36px;\"><![endif]-->\n      <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/compara-servizi/cambio-franco-euro\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;\">\n      <div class=\"rate-box\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b,#334155);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 36px;margin:8px 0 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;\">Tasso CHF → EUR</div>\n        <div class=\"hero-rate\" style=\"font-size:52px;font-weight:900;color:#f97316;letter-spacing:-1px;line-height:1.1;\">0.9420</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;margin-top:4px;color:#22c55e;\">▲ +0.4% vs settimana scorsa</div>\n      </div>\n      </a>\n      <!--[if mso]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n\n      \n      <div style=\"background:rgba(249,115,22,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.3);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 18px;margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;color:#fdba74;\">\n        Su uno stipendio di <strong style=\"color:#f97316;font-size:15px;\">5’000 CHF</strong>, questa settimana guadagni <strong style=\"color:#f97316;font-size:15px;\">€17</strong> in più rispetto a lunedì scorso. In un anno fa <strong style=\"color:#f97316;font-size:15px;\">€910</strong>. Forse vale la pena controllare, no?\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top:12px;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;line-height:1.5;\">Ma se confronti dove cambi, puoi recuperarne <strong style=\"color:#f97316;\">300‑500€</strong>. Non sono noccioline.</div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top:16px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/compara-servizi/cambio-franco-euro\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#f97316;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:8px;\">Confronta i tassi di cambio →</a>\n      </div>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:28px 28px 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 12px;\">Parliamoci chiaro.</div>\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 14px;\">Ogni settimana ti dicono che \"il mercato è volatile\" e che \"bisogna stare attenti\". Grazie, utilissimo. Come dire a uno che sta annegando che l’acqua è bagnata.</p><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 14px;\">Noi preferiamo i numeri. Quelli veri, quelli che trovi in busta paga. Questa settimana: il cambio è a <strong>0.9420</strong>, e c’è una votazione che forse ti sei perso tra un cappuccino e la coda a Brogeda.</p>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;font-style:italic;margin-top:8px;\">— Il team di Frontaliere Ticino, quelli che leggono i cedolini per hobby.</div>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:8px 28px 8px;\">\n      <!--[if mso]><table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\"><![endif]-->\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr class=\"metric-row\">\n        <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 4px 0 0;\">\n          <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 12px;text-align:center;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:22px;margin-bottom:4px;\">💼</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;\">3154</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-top:2px;\">Offerte lavoro</div>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n        <!--[if mso]></td><td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\"><![endif]-->\n        <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 4px;\">\n          <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/statistiche\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 12px;text-align:center;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:22px;margin-bottom:4px;\">📊</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;\">3%</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-top:2px;\">Disoccupazione CH</div>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n        <!--[if mso]></td><td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\"><![endif]-->\n        <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 4px;\">\n          <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/compara-servizi/confronta-casse-malati\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 12px;text-align:center;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:22px;margin-bottom:4px;\">🏥</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;\">CHF 467</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-top:2px;\">Premio LAMal Lugano</div>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n      </tr></table>\n      <!--[if mso]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\n    </td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"padding:12px 28px;\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;\"></div></td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:24px 28px 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;color:#f97316;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 2px;\">💼 Lavoro</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:0;\">Le offerte che non trovi su LinkedIn</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#64748b;margin:4px 0 0;\">Selezionate a mano, non da un algoritmo che pensa che tu voglia fare il \"Growth Hacker\" a Zugo.</div>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:8px 28px 20px;\">\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        \n      <tr><td style=\"padding:0 0 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/concorsi-per-l-assunzione-di-personale-citta-di-lugano-lugano/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n          <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:12px;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td width=\"58\" style=\"padding:16px 0 16px 18px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n                       <img src=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/images/brands/citta-di-lugano.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" alt=\"Città di Lugano\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:10px;display:block;\">\n                     </div>\n              </td>\n              <td style=\"padding:16px 18px 16px 14px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div class=\"job-title\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Concorsi per l'assunzione di personale</div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;\"><a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/azienda-citta-di-lugano\" style=\"color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;\">Città di Lugano</a> · Lugano</div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top:4px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.2);color:#fca5a5;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">🔥 Più cliccata</span> <span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Annuncio attivo</span> <span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Lugano</span></div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </a>\n      </td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:0 0 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/apprendistato-impiegato-a-del-commercio-al-dettaglio-afc-swisscom-sede-ticino-balerna/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n          <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:12px;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td width=\"58\" style=\"padding:16px 0 16px 18px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n                       <img src=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/images/brands/swisscom-sede-ticino.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" alt=\"Swisscom (sede Ticino)\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:10px;display:block;\">\n                     </div>\n              </td>\n              <td style=\"padding:16px 18px 16px 14px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div class=\"job-title\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Apprendistato: Impiegato/a del commercio al dettaglio</div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;\"><a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/azienda-swisscom-sede-ticino\" style=\"color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;\">Swisscom (sede Ticino)</a> · Balerna</div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top:4px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Annuncio attivo</span> <span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Balerna</span></div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </a>\n      </td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:0 0 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/addetti-servizi-alla-casa/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n          <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:12px;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td width=\"58\" style=\"padding:16px 0 16px 18px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n                       <img src=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/images/brands/lis-lugano-istituti-sociali.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" alt=\"LIS – Lugano Istituti Sociali\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:10px;display:block;\">\n                     </div>\n              </td>\n              <td style=\"padding:16px 18px 16px 14px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div class=\"job-title\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Addetti servizi alla casa</div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;\"><a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/azienda-lis-lugano-istituti-sociali\" style=\"color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;\">LIS – Lugano Istituti Sociali</a> · Pregassona</div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top:4px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Annuncio attivo</span> <span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Pregassona</span></div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </a>\n      </td></tr>\n      <tr><td style=\"padding:0 0 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/lavora-con-noi-casale-sa-lugano-ticino/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n          <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:12px;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td width=\"58\" style=\"padding:16px 0 16px 18px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div style=\"width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n                       <img src=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/images/brands/casale.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" alt=\"Casale SA\" style=\"width:44px;height:44px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:10px;display:block;\">\n                     </div>\n              </td>\n              <td style=\"padding:16px 18px 16px 14px;vertical-align:middle;\">\n                <div class=\"job-title\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#f1f5f9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Lavora con noi!</div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:2px;\"><a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino/azienda-casale-sa\" style=\"color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;\">Casale SA</a> · Lugano, Ticino</div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top:4px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Annuncio attivo</span> <span style=\"font-size:10px;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.15);color:#fdba74;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:600;\">Lugano, Ticino</span></div>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </a>\n      </td></tr>\n        <tr><td style=\"text-align:center;padding-top:14px;\">\n          <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/cerca-lavoro-ticino\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:transparent;border:2px solid #f97316;color:#f97316;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;padding:11px 28px;border-radius:8px;\">Tutte le 3154 offerte →</a>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"padding:8px 28px 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f97316,#ea580c);border-radius:12px;padding:20px 22px;text-align:center;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;\">“In Svizzera, il salario mediano è di circa 6.665 CHF al mese (2022).”</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin-top:6px;\">— UST</div>\n      </div>\n    </td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"padding:12px 28px;\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;\"></div></td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:24px 28px 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;color:#f97316;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 2px;\">📰 Da leggere</div>\n    </td></tr>\n    <tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background:#ffffff;padding:0 28px 8px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://frontaliereticino.ch/articoli-frontaliere/votazioni-imposizione-ticino-2026\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;\">\n          <div style=\"width:100%;height:200px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 50%,#f97316 100%);text-align:center;line-height:200px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-size:56px;letter-spacing:8px;\">🗳️ 🏔️ 🇨🇭</span>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"padding:18px 20px;\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:8px;\">🔥 Più letto</span>\n            <div style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.3;\">Votazioni cantonali Ticino 2026: cosa cambia per i frontalieri</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;margin:0 0 14px;\">SSR, imposizione individuale, fondo climatico: 4 temi su cui voti (o dovresti). Ecco cosa significa per il tuo portafoglio.</div>\n            <span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0f172a;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:8px;\">Leggi l’analisi completa →</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n    </td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"padding:12px 28px;\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;\"></div></td></tr><tr><td class=\"section-pad\" style=\"background